<view class="page history-page">
  <view class="history-head">
    <view>
      <view class="eyebrow">按天归档</view>
      <view class="title">轨迹历史</view>
    </view>
    <view class="count-pill">{{days.length}} 天</view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{days.length}}" class="day-list">
    <view
      wx:for="{{days}}"
      wx:key="date"
      class="day-card"
      data-date="{{item.date}}"
      bindtap="openDay"
    >
      <view class="day-main">
        <view>
          <view class="day-date">{{item.date}}</view>
          <view class="day-week">{{item.week}} · {{item.points}} 个轨迹点</view>
        </view>
        <view class="arrow">›</view>
      </view>
      <view class="summary-row">
        <view>
          <text class="summary-value">{{item.distance}}</text>
          <text class="summary-label">距离</text>
        </view>
        <view>
          <text class="summary-value">{{item.duration}}</text>
          <text class="summary-label">时长</text>
        </view>
        <view>
          <text class="summary-value">{{item.checkins}}</text>
          <text class="summary-label">打卡</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:else class="empty history-empty">
    还没有保存过轨迹。回到今日页打开记录开关，第一条路线就会出现在这里。
  </view>
</view>
